Dynamic Frontend Components

Essential Components to Build:

Product Listing Component: Display products dynamically in a grid layout.

Product Detail Component: Show individual product details with routing.

Category Component: Enable filtering products by category.

Search Bar: Implement search functionality.

Cart Component: Manage added items and calculate total price.

Checkout Flow Component: Multi-step form for order placement.

User Profile Component: Show user details and order history.

Admin Dashboard: Manage products, orders, and discounts.

Discount & Promotion Component: Display dynamic discounts.

